    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/8d7b600df2309a0a688b32ca312e1e49.poster.avif?t=1704680134\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/8d7b600df2309a0a688b32ca312e1e49.webm?t=1704680134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/8d7b600df2309a0a688b32ca312e1e49.mp4?t=1704680134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stoner Fueled Roleplaying Adventure</strong></h2>Hell’s Mouth is a <strong>stoner fueled</strong> single-player <strong>RPG</strong> where you live a life as a cannabis user looking to earn some cash. You get to <strong>grow</strong> weed, <strong>sell</strong> weed and of course <strong>smoke</strong> weed. The game includes <strong>minigames</strong> for grinding, growing and rolling weed. The main gameplay is a <strong>top-down</strong> adventure through-out a city inspired by Helmond. You collect resources and fight enemies while going on all sorts of <strong>quests</strong> earning yourself skill points for the next upgrade you treat yourself with.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/c9f696e582403f2a876c110a2c3487f6.poster.avif?t=1704680134\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/c9f696e582403f2a876c110a2c3487f6.webm?t=1704680134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/c9f696e582403f2a876c110a2c3487f6.mp4?t=1704680134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You make your own story</strong></h2>In this game you can <strong>customize</strong> your character’s gender, hair, clothing and coloring in any way you like, but that’s not all. The joints you roll are in fact a <strong>customizable power up</strong> you crafted yourself. Unlock the abilities in the skilltree to roll any kind of tip, find yourself the cannabis strain with the best effects for your situation, and be prepared for your next encounter.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/19a6ce351902047e7af08eca15138438.poster.avif?t=1704680134\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/19a6ce351902047e7af08eca15138438.webm?t=1704680134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/19a6ce351902047e7af08eca15138438.mp4?t=1704680134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/fb00e200169419e2e491e246027c3271.poster.avif?t=1704680134\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/fb00e200169419e2e491e246027c3271.webm?t=1704680134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/fb00e200169419e2e491e246027c3271.mp4?t=1704680134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game contains all sorts of items to supplement <strong>smoking</strong> and <strong>growing</strong>, as well as a bunch of iconic dutch products such as energy drinks. While playing you will get to meet all sorts of <strong>cultures</strong> and people living in Hell’s Mouth. Not all drugs get treated the same way by the law in Hell’s Mouth, which constructs conflict in the city. <strong>Criminal activity</strong> is rising and you are in the middle of the action.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/da57ae086ba862ba23e3f411a6e4e808.poster.avif?t=1704680134\" width=600 height=686 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/da57ae086ba862ba23e3f411a6e4e808.webm?t=1704680134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153710/extras/da57ae086ba862ba23e3f411a6e4e808.mp4?t=1704680134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
